---
export interface Props {
  title?: string;
  subtitle?: string;
}

---

<section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-[calc(100vh-102px)] py-7">
  <div class="flex flex-row justify-center  w-full h-full px-[var(--x-axis-main-content-padding)] sm:px-[var(--x-axis-main-content-padding-sm)] lg:px-[var(--x-axis-main-content-padding-lg)]">
    <div class="min-w-0 flex flex-8 flex-col items-start  w-auto h-full  justify-between">
      
      <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col space-y-2  justify-center">

      <h1 class="text-7xl font-medium text-nord0 font-sans leading-24">
        ¿Cansado de 
        <br> 

        <span class="bg-gradient-to-tl from-nord9 to-nord10 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold">perder</span> el <span class="bg-gradient-to-tr from-nord9 to-nord10 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold">tiempo</span> 
        <br>
        facturando
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-nord9 to-nord10 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold"> tickets</span>?
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-nord0 font-sans leading-9">
        Factura tus tickets en piloto automático
      </p>

      <p class="text-xl text-nord0/60 font-sans leading-9">

        Deja de perder dinero por no facturar tickets a tiempo. TeFacturo está
        <br> pensado para que pequeños y medianos empresarios puedan delegar la
        <br> facturación de sus tickets y concentrarse en lo que de verdad importa:
        <br> su negocio. Nos encargamos de tus responsabilidades tediosas y repetitvas 
        <br> para que te puedas enfocar en lo que de verdad importa.

       </p>

    </div>

        <div id="company-moving-logos" class="relative w-full max-w-[85%] overflow-hidden mb-4" style="mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, black 20%, black 80%, transparent); -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, black 20%, black 80%, transparent);">
          <div class="flex flex-row space-x-3 w-max animate-scroll">
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>  
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full"></div>
            <!-- duplicate set for seamless loop -->
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>  
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="min-h-12 min-w-36 bg-nord10 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="min-w-0 flex flex-6 flex-col items-center justify-center w-auto h-full ">
      <img 
        src="/assets/elements/Hand4Website.png" 
        alt="Mano ilustrada para la web"
        class="max-w-full max-h-full object-contain"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
